Global Tokens

primary

The main color for interactive elements and to draw a user's attention.

secondary

success

Use this color to signify that something good has happened

warn

Use this color to draw the user's attention to minor problems they need to address

critical

Use this color to indicate mission-critical problems that must be addressed, and to signify destructive actions
